---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy — What Is The Govt Saying" description="Privacy policy for whatisthegovtsaying.com">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <h1 class="font-headline text-2xl sm:text-[1.75rem] font-medium mb-8">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <div class="prose space-y-5">
      <p>
        <strong>What we collect:</strong> Nothing. This site does not use cookies, analytics, tracking scripts, or any form of user data collection. There are no accounts, no forms, and no JavaScript that phones home.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>How summaries are made:</strong> Government press releases are collected from official public sources. Summaries are generated by bots (language models) and may contain errors or omissions. Every summary links to the original source so you can verify the information yourself.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Third parties:</strong> This site is hosted as static files. No third-party services are loaded in your browser.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Changes:</strong> If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <a href="/" class="font-ui text-sm text-(--color-ink-muted) hover:text-(--color-accent-1) no-underline transition-colors">&larr; Back to digest</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
